comments: Great guy, more than patient in office hours. It\'s a hard subject to be sure, but you can tell that he does his best and doesn\'t get offended at the little things.

First of all I still don\'t know how I managed to get a B in this class while thinking C- was the best I could do. Miracle?Curve was definitely huge. Noone understood the contents he taught, well minus the exceptions. There was no book. He wrote out 2 page long calculus equations and then didn\'t grade on it on exams. No correlation b/w exam and hw.
great teacher! explains game theory in a clear and simple way. take this class with him
